S.FORM: Norway Gaga kska Owcow ka Norway, 62 00 N, 10 00 E ka gaga na nniqan. Kana ka knlbangan na o 323,802 sq km (hangan na o Tg68) (knlbanga dxgal o 304,282 sq km, knlbangan qsiya o 19,520 sq km). Kana ka sejiqun o niqan 5,550,203 hiyi.(2024) Gaga Oslo ka pusu alang paru, jiyax 17 idas 5 ka jiyax skrayan klwaan. Manu ka dxgal Norway ga wada sugan 2.70 ka dxgal qpahan, 27.80 ka dxgal bbuyu, rahuq dxgal do niqan 69.50 na. Bukung klwaan ta sayang o kiya ka Harald V, pnaah hngkawas 1991 idas 1 jiyax 17 pnrajing kmlawa klwaan.
